In the ser-vice of the heav-en-ly king, we must keep step from the first, Go keep step; step in time;
While you an-swer to the mu-sic of the, When we for-get the pain which the cap-tains have borne, Yet march ev-er- in
His is the cross of the brave that holds all things here; we'll keep step, and we'll keep step all the time.
